title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 12 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 12 2022
description:
Blake Masters, Arizona Senate candidate, joins Clay and Buck to discuss Biden's newest illegal gun grab, the Democrat-caused illegal immigration flood, Elon Musk, and how to counter Bidenflation. Will Elon Musk take over Twitter? U.K. Prime Minister Boris Johnson walks the war-torn streets of Kiev with President Zelensky. C&B wonder, why isn't safe for Biden to do that? And they remind us that Biden still hasn't visited the U.S. southern border. Prepare for the return of the mask mandates. Update on the Brooklyn subway mass shooting.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
